{"tid":1780973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小特朗普轟《時代》離棄香港抗爭者 前比利時首相：我選香港","createTime":"2019-12-12T21:24:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T13:35:48.000Z","uid":125193,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"10e870516384a37a169697fda5a382478d7ffa58","tid":1780973,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T21:24:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191212/60368802?utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=share_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191212%2F60368802%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&d=Vh0AUGqI%2BhuKY3uG7C8Fc2LZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=f6e1cdef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191212%2F60368802%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&h=74679d41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191212/60368802?utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=share_link</a><br />\n<br />\n【新增動新聞】瑞典16歲環保少女通貝里（Greta Thunberg）獲選為美國《時代》周刊2019年度風雲人物，在國際間有不少討論，有「小特朗普」之稱的特朗普長子唐納德（Donald Trump Jr.）批評《時代》離棄（leaves out）香港抗爭者，比利時前首相也在Twitter發文，稱個人會選擇香港示威者。另外，特朗普周四在社交網發文，稱通貝里必須處理其控制憤怒的問題，然後與朋友去看一套老氣的電影，着通貝里「去晃晃吧」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唐納德在Twitter發文說：「《時代》離棄那些為自己性命和自由而戰的香港示威者，去推銷一個被用作營銷噱頭的少女。你們怎敢這麼做？」唐納德用了通貝里9月在聯合國氣候行動峯會上，嚴厲譴責各國領袖的名言「你們怎麼敢這麼做」（How dare you），來反擊《時代》周刊。<br />\n<br />\n《時代》編輯今年選出通貝里為年度風雲人物，不過解釋選擇通貝里的理據時，也兩度提及香港，指她代表新一代自己危機自己救的時代精神。<br />\n此外，比利時前首相、歐洲議會議員伏思達（Guy Verhofstadt）亦發文說，他個人會選擇香港爭取民主的示威者做年度風雲人物，不過認為通貝里也值得獲頒這個頭銜，他希望這有助將氣候危機的訊息傳播開去。"},{"pid":"0532741b887912646281cb87f3d1730cf621a99e","tid":1780973,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T21:26:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fa1fa2a2f50839dd778da0d0523cc6288b01f858","tid":1780973,"uid":124400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T21:27:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cdc92ef5e227c2be9ea352d496cb39e7add64a1","tid":1780973,"uid":34643,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T21:32:26.000Z","msg":"time係唔係借香港插環保少女?"},{"pid":"bbf88279c0242231cfe472995cae4f636f5b1062","tid":1780973,"uid":56729,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9cdc92ef5e227c2be9ea352d496cb39e7add64a1","tid":1780973,"uid":34643,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T21:32:26.000Z","msg":"time係唔係借香港插環保少女?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T21:37:23.000Z","msg":"都可以話係以退為進<br />\n我地借力打力就啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75ec3cdaf34a2f825b016f9b1ad09861e382f93d","tid":1780973,"uid":16055,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T21:59:31.000Z","msg":"無自由談何環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27c5d25beb6de74fa4380c8f185cabe6702bf088","tid":1780973,"uid":238370,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T22:02:21.000Z",